# Overview

This pipeline scrapes Basketball Reference, builds a **Bayesian linear regression**
model to predict what each player *should* earn based on their on-court production,
and compares predicted salaries to actual contracts and free agent signings.

**Output:** an Excel file with three tabs — All Contracts, FA Unsigned, FA Signed.

