# Step 3 — Load 2026 Free Agent List from GitHub

The NBA FA tracker page is JavaScript-rendered and cannot be scraped with `rvest`.
The full list (213 players, sourced from `nba.com/players/free-agent-tracker/2026`)
is stored as a CSV in the project GitHub repo and loaded here.

**To update next offseason:** replace the CSV on GitHub with the new FA list.

```{r load-fa-list, cache=TRUE}
fa_all <- read.csv(FA_CSV_URL, stringsAsFactors = FALSE) %>%
  mutate(Player = clean_name(Player))

cat(sprintf("Free agents loaded from GitHub: %d\n", nrow(fa_all)))
print(head(fa_all, 5))
```

